This paper deals with multilingual question answering, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. The paper discusses different methods of translation and builds a model to learn optimal feature weights. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning, which suggests sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with multilingual data, which could also fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
